title: Savoy lauds comeback against Brave Warriors 10 October 2015 (Confédération Africaine de Football)
text: ( Source : Confédération Africaine de Football ) 10 October 2015 02:35 Gambia coach Raoul Savoy has lauded his team's spirited comeback after what he called a catastrophic first period against Namibia in a FIFA World Cup Russia 2018 first
